(115, 'Nike Air', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5/da036020-3b7e-4a92-b13f-f0af3eba4307/air-big-kids-boys-french-terry-pullover-hoodie-fC1sBH.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/25f8db55-ff14-4478-b1d1-5d8a88457111/air-big-kids-boys-french-terry-pullover-hoodie-fC1sBH.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/cdbbf563-e3fa-42d1-bd0b-62aee37f2fb3/air-big-kids-boys-french-terry-pullover-hoodie-fC1sBH.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/c275e811-5cd9-4542-b325-de9fc3029674/air-big-kids-boys-french-terry-pullover-hoodie-fC1sBH.jpg', 'We love Air as much as you do. The Nike Air Hoodie shows big brand love on your grab-and-go pullover to make it an easy fit into your weekly rotation.', 60, 10, 'Big Kids\' (Boys\') French Terry Pullover Hoodie', 2, 3),
(116, 'Nike Trophy', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5/45f485ee-95b9-4489-82c9-80691c2a0a05/trophy-big-kids-boys-printed-training-shorts-4XqV7f.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/70869530-9fda-4177-b743-8fc15e3b3abd/trophy-big-kids-boys-printed-training-shorts-4XqV7f.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/5a680c25-c8a2-4432-8a23-9adfea3ffbbd/trophy-big-kids-boys-printed-training-shorts-4XqV7f.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/32475963-3ce2-47e9-80f5-19baca927882/trophy-big-kids-boys-printed-training-shorts-4XqV7f.jpg', 'Your favorite sport awaits when you pull on the Nike Trophy Shorts. They’re powered by Dri-FIT, plus adjust for a perfectly snug fit while you run, jump and play.', 20, 50, 'Big Kids\' (Boys\') Printed Training Shorts', 3, 3),
(117, 'Nike Sportswear', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5/8fab10e2-75c0-4784-8698-7022be40cb2d/sportswear-big-kids-girls-graphic-full-zip-hoodie-rKNJ97.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/47d787c9-f28c-44e0-942f-18cdbc48af58/sportswear-big-kids-girls-graphic-full-zip-hoodie-rKNJ97.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/5bce2798-cf07-4794-97f3-213de83dc3e9/sportswear-big-kids-girls-graphic-full-zip-hoodie-rKNJ97.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/f6ec1f13-7d88-4240-be49-d49eb2e738e4/sportswear-big-kids-girls-graphic-full-zip-hoodie-rKNJ97.jpg', 'Stay a little more cozy with the Nike Sportswear Hoodie. Whether you’re playing outside or kicking back at home, this zip-up will feel comfy anywhere. Plus, we’ve added a colorful design and front pockets to give a lil’ extra to a classic.', 50, 50, 'Nike Sportswear Big Kids\' (Girls\') Graphic Full-Zi', 2, 3),
