(126, 'Nike Gym Club', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5/858c3427-18a7-4953-95a9-d954f3055f96/gym-club-kids-duffel-bag-DNTBjb81.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/28d531a8-70c2-4ed2-b222-78a44f8e585c/gym-club-kids-duffel-bag-DNTBjb81.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/67d3c200-b4f6-4bc3-a020-122becca4657/gym-club-kids-duffel-bag-DNTBjb81.jpg', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,q_80/ff0afa60-ec2f-4e8d-aa45-08a5e249d24a/gym-club-kids-duffel-bag-DNTBjb81.jpg', 'The Nike Gym Club Bag has you set for practice, the game or your next adventure. This duffel has a full-zip main compartment with inside pockets to keep you organized. Carry it by hand or around your shoulders so your gear is always close.', 25, 50, 'Kids\' Duffel Bag', 4, 3),
